data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful 3 level, 3 bedroom, 4 bath Reston townhome. The main level includes a freshly renovated half bath and a renovated kitchen with stainless steel appliances, brand new dishwasher and brand new quartz countertops installed in 2024.  Upstairs boasts three bedrooms and two full bathrooms. The basements includes a den with a gorgeous fireplace and a bonus room that would make an excellent study or extra bedroom. There is new carpet in the bedrooms and basement and new  LVP throughout the main level, bathrooms and the bonus study.   Rest assured, this home has been meticulously maintained, with a new roof installed in 2021, providing both peace of mind and aesthetic appeal. The entire home has been freshly repainted. There is also a brand new dishwasher and brand new quartz countertops installed in 2024. The entire home is bathed in a warm and inviting glow, courtesy of the new lighting fixtures that have been thoughtfully installed throughout. Every detail has been attended to, with new outlets and light switches adorning every room. New water heater installed 2023.   Conveniently situated off Fairfax County Parkway, this residence is a mere stone's throw away from the vibrant Reston Town Center.  Parking is a breeze, with two assigned spaces conveniently marked (65) in front of the house. It is worth noting that the HOA fee is $295.00 per quarter, while the Reston Association fee amounts to $771.00 annually. Allow yourself to be embraced by the charm and grace of this exceptional townhome, where relaxation and convenience converge.
